plot: Ma and the kids head back to the Ozarks for a visit with Uncle Sedge (essentially a Pa Kettle replacement). He's working his way through a twenty years long relationship with Miss Bedelia Baines.   Written by  Ed Stephan
title: The Kettles in the Ozarks
